The footage, captured by John Arcequie, shows a number of cops running onto the platform. One officer can be heard shouting at the people inside Myrtle-Willoughby Avenues station to 'get on the floor' as his colleagues conduct their search.

As officers run into the station, Arcequie can be heard saying 'Yo this is crazy. Y'all seeing this?' Seconds later a woman can be heard starting to cry and he  can be heard trying to comfort her.

